<h2>Brew Method: Clever</h2>
<div>
    <div  class=brewimage>
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-clever.png" %>
    </div>
  <p>
    The clever is a hybrid full-immersion and filtered brew method. Keeping the best features from the french press and the pour over, but removing the drawbacks by controlling the amount of steeping time, and filtering out the suspended grit. Key identifiers are  a full bodied and smooth finish.
  </p>
</div>





