<h3>Instructions</h3>
<div>
  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-instructions-clever1.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsleft>1. Fold the filter paper at the seam and place it in a clean cone.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-instructions-clever2.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsright>2. Preheat water and using a slender spout water kettle, pour into clever to rinse filter paper and then decant into the mug to warm.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-instructions-clever3.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsleft>3. Measure beans on a scale according to the bean water ratio and grind beans in a burr grinder. Place fresh grounds into the pre-rinsed clever and give it a gentle shake to flatten the bed of grounds. Tare the scale.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-instructions-clever4.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsright>4. Starting at the center, pour the water in a slow and even spiral over the grounds to fully saturate the beans and remove air pockets. Start the timer and let bloom for 30sec.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-instructions-clever5.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsleft>5. Using the scale to measure, continue to pour the remaining water ratio over the grounds. Let steep for an additional 3-4 min depending on preferred extraction time and grind.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-instructions-clever6.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsright>6. Discard pre-heat water from warming mug. Place the clever on drinking vessel to decant the brew. When the last drops are free from the clever, remove brew vessel from the mug. Enjoy.</p>
  </div>
</div>

